node.text:
Babe, Italy is now a description word in my book!:) When I think of Italy, I think of Joy & Love. You planned the best trip! This was truly an unforgettable 5 Year Anniversary! You’re the best Partner. My Best Friend! Mi Amore.  I love you so much! 
Ti Amo Tanto. 
❤️🇮🇹

node.text: In celebration of my @Bet Her Award Nomination for my song #Rooted featuring @EsterDean, I want to Celebrate MY FANS. It was so much fun having some of you in this Viral clip I did with @Thomeography and @Jamaicacraft and some incredible dancers! My Melanin Queens, My Black Queens, All Queens shining! You brought your babies and all! This truly warmed my heart.. I did my part just 2 weeks after giving birth.. I was pushing and having fun! It’s All Rooted in Me. Rooted in You. Rooted in Us! Keep on Dancin’ #StayRooted #Dance

node.title: It’s Rooted in You 😎 Me and My Fans Jamin! 💃🏽

node.text:
It’s our goal to create Good Brands that embody love, respect & care. We hope our words, and more importantly our actions, inspire you. 
#itbeginswithone @thehouseoflrc. The House anthem was Created by @jamalparkerr
Join us! 
@thehouseoflrc
Love, 
Russell & Ciara
